If he's drifted that

17:42.680 --> 17:44.440
way, he wouldn't
recognize me anyway.

17:45.000 --> 17:48.040
Like having a
brother, but not really.

17:50.920 --> 17:52.920
Did you find out who Sally is?

17:53.320 --> 17:55.040
