-What?

23:21.000 --> 23:21.960
Where did you study

23:22.080 --> 23:23.040
West Point, Harvard Med.

23:23.160 --> 23:25.680
I learned printing associations from
the Boy Scouts.  Was stupid.  Sorry

23:26.040 --> 23:27.000
You should be fired.

23:27.120 --> 23:28.320
Fortunately, I
don't work for you.

23:28.440 --> 23:29.400
No.  You should fire me.

23:29.520 --> 23:30.480
-Dr.  Piel...
-No!

23:30.680 --> 23:32.480
I am grateful for
what you want to do

23:32.760 --> 23:34.480
but I've got special
treatment all my life.

23:35.080 --> 23:36.680
I don't want this.

23:38.400 --> 23:39.640
