23:40.080 --> 23:41.440
I only checked
the pulse manually.

23:44.480 --> 23:46.480
You don't tell the family
about it, understand?

23:47.120 --> 23:48.960
You stay calm until I
have spoken to the council

23:49.080 --> 23:50.800
and until the pathology
examines the leg.

23:51.720 --> 23:53.120
That would be all, Dr.  Piel.

23:57.320 --> 23:58.480
She is still young.

23:58.600 --> 24:01.600
But she made a big
mistake that cost him his leg.

24:02.120 --> 24:04.280
And we come into the
crosshairs of a process.

24:04.800 --> 24:06.040
And you want to protect them.

24:06.160 --> 24:07.920
It won't help her or you.

24:09.320 --> 24:11.160
We will notify your officer.

24:12.520 --> 24:15.480
You're welcome.  Then
maybe I'll get to where I belong.

24:30.360 --> 24:32.160
Once upon a time there was a boy

24:34.720 --> 24:38.280
A strangely enchanted boy

24:40.480 --> 24:43.840
They say he wandered very far

24:45.040 --> 24:46.600
Very far

24:48.080 --> 24:51.000
Over land and sea

24:52.080 --> 24:53.720
A little bit shy

24:55.800 --> 24:57.560
With sad eyes

24:59.720 --> 25:01.560
But very wise

25:02.840 --> 25:04.680
He was

25:13.720 --> 25:15.440
Two doctors didn't notice

25:16.440 --> 25:18.320
and one of them
did a pelvic exam.

25:21.680 --> 25:23.960
-She is a beautiful woman.
-Yes.

25:24.880 --> 25:25.920
That is her.

25:27.120 --> 25:29.080
We've only been a
couple for a few months

25:30.320 --> 25:33.640
but i was so in love...

25:33.760 --> 25:36.720
Many different people come
here every day.  Hundreds.

25:37.560 --> 25:39.120
On the worst day of your life

25:39.480 --> 25:41.080
they all have one thing in common.

25:41.880 --> 25:44.880
They need someone
else to look after them.

25:45.360 --> 25:46.720
Do you know what that taught me?

25:47.600 --> 25:51.440
We are all the same.

25:52.280 --> 25:53.640
All of us.

25:57.680 --> 26:01.280
I didn't know when
to say I wasn't 38.

26:01.520 --> 26:04.640
Now would be a good time.

26:12.080 --> 26:14.720
The urinary
catheter is in place.

26:14.920 --> 26:16.280
I'm sorry if that hurt.

26:16.760 --> 26:19.240
Shouldn't the liquid
be yellow like urine?

26:21.360 --> 26:24.160
This is pus.  Oh my God.
Everything full of pus.

26:24.640 --> 26:25.720
What do you mean by pus?

26:25.840 --> 26:28.920
Infection.  An infection.
Do not worry.  I do that.

26:29.040 --> 26:32.160
-You need to calm down.
-I am.  I am totally calm.

26:32.640 --> 26:35.520
-I feel dizzy.
-Beth?

26:35.640 --> 26:38.520
Beth!  Stay awake.
It's a septic shock.

26:38.800 --> 26:40.440
You have to go to the Center Stage.
And now.

