-I do not need much.
-Stop drinking.

27:07.960 --> 27:09.640
Now are you teaching me

27:09.760 --> 27:11.600
I have changed.  I grew up.

27:12.080 --> 27:13.520
You have no idea who I am

27:14.640 --> 27:16.680
Only I know, buddy.

27:20.760 --> 27:21.960
Come on, Mario.

27:23.360 --> 27:25.040
Suction!

27:26.000 --> 27:27.160
Suction!

27:29.040 --> 27:30.200
What's happening?

27:30.400 --> 27:31.360
Probably bleeding varices.

