28:26.120 --> 28:27.760
That's what happens
when you're an alcoholic.

28:32.040 --> 28:33.400
It's collapsing folks.

28:33.520 --> 28:35.120
Get 40 ready.  It has to work!

28:35.240 --> 28:36.920
She has no veins.
As if everyone had shrunk.

