29:59.840 --> 30:03.640
You may feel
phantom pain, it hurts.

30:04.200 --> 30:05.920
We can help you then.

30:06.680 --> 30:10.080
Mirror field therapy,
nerve cuff stimulation.

30:10.640 --> 30:11.880
Are you my doctor now?

30:12.040 --> 30:13.280
One of them, yes.

