Of course not.

30:38.080 --> 30:39.040
Here.

30:54.120 --> 30:55.240
Wow!

30:56.400 --> 30:57.960
I don't want to lie, this is...

31:00.320 --> 31:01.480
That's shocking.

31:07.520 --> 31:09.360
I'm sorry for my dad.

31:12.120 --> 31:14.640
He acts so cool...

31:17.680 --> 31:19.200
But he's devastated.

31:20.920 --> 31:22.720
He had high hopes for me.

31:25.320 --> 31:27.240
-I have to tell you something.
-Charlotte!

