31:59.880 --> 32:02.280
Maybe that contributed
to this, I don't know.

32:02.400 --> 32:03.960
Maybe during the
pelvic exam I...

32:04.080 --> 32:06.120
No no.
You're making a fool of yourself.

32:06.240 --> 32:08.680
So. I have to see my patients.

32:11.080 --> 32:12.800
Come on, sugar
bears, let's go for a walk.

32:15.400 --> 32:17.520
Does he react to the
vasopressors, Dr.  Pineda?

32:17.840 --> 32:18.880
No.

32:20.080 --> 32:22.520
Alice asked us to
remove the breathing tube

32:22.640 --> 32:23.880
so that it would be
more comfortable for him.

32:24.560 --> 32:26.080
