32:26.440 --> 32:28.160
He keeps going unconscious.

32:28.440 --> 32:30.200
I just don't want
him to be in pain.

32:30.880 --> 32:32.160
He doesn't have that.

32:35.080 --> 32:37.320
Are the toxicological
findings there?

32:38.160 --> 32:39.280
Yes he is.

32:40.800 --> 32:41.760
Alice?

32:43.200 --> 32:45.720
-Alice?
-Yes, Dale.  I'm here honey

32:45.920 --> 32:47.440
There was an accident.

32:48.120 --> 32:49.400
I had an accident.

32:51.160 --> 32:52.120
Yes.

32:52.360 --> 32:53.840
Did i run over someone?

32:55.680 --> 32:58.240
Honey, please calm down.

32:58.360 --> 32:59.720
Did someone die?

33:03.880 --> 33:04.920
No.

33:07.120 --> 33:08.360
Nobody died.

33:14.280 --> 33:15.640
Just take a rest.

33:19.920 --> 33:20.880
Dr.  Rorish.

33:23.320 --> 33:24.520
Why did you do that?

33:25.000 --> 33:27.360
The finding indicated amphetamines.

33:27.480 --> 33:30.680
They always tell us
not to lie to patients.

33:31.200 --> 33:33.560
Why are you doing it now?
Just with him?

33:34.920 --> 33:35.960
I dont know.

33:36.560 --> 33:38.760
He's already paying
the ultimate price.

33:39.720 --> 33:41.480
I wanted mercy.

33:55.360 --> 33:56.440
What's happening?

33:57.320 --> 33:58.520
You are in the hospital

33:59.680 --> 34:00.880
Liver failure...

34:02.280 --> 34:04.880
This causes the veins in the
esophagus to swell and bleed.

34:05.000 --> 34:06.040
You almost died.

34:06.880 --> 34:07.840
We stopped the bleeding.

34:07.960 --> 34:09.679
But we have to watch
you for a while longer.

34:09.840 --> 34:10.920
Now...

34:19.239 --> 34:20.920
You think you are
better than me, don't you?

34:22.199 --> 34:23.639
But you are not.

34:24.920 --> 34:26.719
You're a con man
and everyone knows it.

34:28.880 --> 34:31.199
You are so disappointing.

34:33.760 --> 34:36.280
But right now I'm your doctor.

35:00.720 --> 35:01.800
Do you have a moment?

35:02.520 --> 35:04.320
-Clear.
-Come in guys.

35:05.080 --> 35:07.760
These are Captains Quinn and
Gibson of the US Medical Corps.

35:08.040 --> 35:09.280
New Prosthetics Department.

35:11.800 --> 35:13.000
It's a Pentagon program.

35:13.480 --> 35:15.480
They revolutionize prostheses

35:15.600 --> 35:16.600
with state-of-the-art solutions.

35:17.040 --> 35:19.160
Can we take it slow?
He needs some time.

35:19.480 --> 35:21.040
-What's this?
-The?

35:21.840 --> 35:24.240
This is a great next
generation robotic arm.

35:24.560 --> 35:25.680
It has 26 limbs

35:26.280 --> 35:27.800
can withstand up to 20 kilos,

35:28.040 --> 35:29.240
you control it with your

35:29.360 --> 35:30.520
head, like a regular arm.

35:32.160 --> 35:33.240
But i need a leg.

35:33.840 --> 35:34.800
We have legs.

35:35.240 --> 35:36.680
We have many legs.

35:37.200 --> 35:38.360
Captain Quinn?

35:55.440 --> 35:57.320
The antibiotics are working.

35:57.920 --> 35:59.960
Oh, you are not pregnant
in case you were unsure.

36:00.600 --> 36:01.560
Very funny.

36:02.840 --> 36:04.600
Explain it to me.
You were a...

36:04.920 --> 36:07.160
Straight man turned woman

36:07.560 --> 36:11.320
who is now a lesbian?
Do I understand that right?

36:11.440 --> 36:12.840
I've always loved women

36:13.720 --> 36:15.560
that didn't change
when I became one.

36:15.840 --> 36:17.760
And it's not that
complicated at all.

36:18.320 --> 36:20.800
It sounds like the
Pythagorean theorem to you.

36:22.000 --> 36:22.960
Fine

36:24.080 --> 36:25.080
I get it.

36:26.400 --> 36:28.680
There are some who
don't understand me either.

36:30.360 --> 36:31.840
What do you not understand?

36:33.080 --> 36:34.120
Everything.

36:40.760 --> 36:42.520
-Hi.
-Can you knock?

36:43.680 --> 36:44.840
It's a curtain.

36:46.000 --> 36:47.240
And...

36:48.520 --> 36:49.640
I'm so sorry.

36:50.720 --> 36:52.240
That's a lot at once.

36:52.800 --> 36:54.160
I'm so sorry.

36:54.920 --> 36:57.120
I wanted to tell you.
I was just scared.

36:58.680 --> 37:01.640
I wanted you to
see me for who I am

37:02.520 --> 37:05.440
not as the man the
world always saw me as.

37:06.000 --> 37:08.280
How could I have seen you?

37:12.480 --> 37:13.600
Do you know why i love you

37:14.120 --> 37:17.040
Because you're the first
person I feel real with.

37:18.560 --> 37:21.000
-Is that the other way around?
-Naturally.

37:23.080 --> 37:25.200
Wait... did you just
say you love me?

37:26.960 --> 37:28.400
Yes, silly.

37:29.920 --> 37:31.080
I love you too.

37:46.840 --> 37:48.360
We slept even during the war.

37:50.280 --> 37:52.280
Good night dr  Willis.

37:52.680 --> 37:54.240
-Will Charlotte make it?
-No idea.

37:55.320 --> 37:57.640
-Will Campbell fire you?
-I didn't say.

37:57.840 --> 37:59.240
They asked if she could do it.

37:59.840 --> 38:01.880
How many don't
make it into the army?

38:02.000 --> 38:03.200
Seven out of ten.

38:03.320 --> 38:04.400
It should be that way.

38:04.560 --> 38:06.200
There is too much
at stake, it has to be.

38:06.480 --> 38:08.200
They said she had what it takes.

38:08.320 --> 38:09.360
She did.

38:10.040 --> 38:12.880
Now let's see if she
has what it takes to stay.

38:14.560 --> 38:16.360
-What about you?
-What about me?

38:17.720 --> 38:18.920
Why are you here?

38:19.040 --> 38:20.520
I owe the army two years.

38:21.120 --> 38:23.480
They keep me working here
until my assignment is over.

38:23.600 --> 38:25.480
-How so?
-Long story.

38:26.200 --> 38:27.480
I'm not giving up on Charlotte.

38:28.080 --> 38:29.960
-Good.
-Good night.

38:30.640 --> 38:31.840
Night.

38:36.760 --> 38:39.960
Dr.  Piel.  You did it.

38:40.560 --> 38:41.720
Give us a moment

38:43.440 --> 38:44.440
Are you all right?

38:45.960 --> 38:47.520
I shouldn't be here.

38:48.680 --> 38:51.240
He'll talk to his team.
His doctors should be there.

38:51.880 --> 38:53.480
But I'm the reason we're here

38:53.640 --> 38:54.880
His leg was shattered.

38:55.480 --> 38:57.280
There was no way you
could have changed that.

38:58.480 --> 38:59.600
Nevertheless...

39:00.440 --> 39:02.960
People?  Are you coming

39:04.360 --> 39:05.400
Dr.  Piel...

39:06.200 --> 39:07.720
Your patient is asking about you.

39:22.920 --> 39:24.360
He didn't mean it that way.

39:24.640 --> 39:25.800
You're a nice guy, Angus.

39:25.920 --> 39:27.880
How can he be disappointed?
You are a doctor!
